---
description: Agent Security workspace review rules
globs: **/*
alwaysApply: false
---

Use Agent Security for sensitive changes.

- Never store real secrets.
- Auth, permission, admin, token, credential, deploy, webhook, registry, and MCP changes need evidence.
- Record risk, owner, and rollback or mitigation.
- Run `node .opendock/harness/opendock__agent-security/check.mjs` before handoff when possible.
